<style>
  /* Keep accordion behavior consistent with brand colors */
  .accordion-button:focus { box-shadow: none; }
  .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) { box-shadow: none; }
  .border-yellow .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) { background: var(--yellow-translucent); }
  .border-purple .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) { background: var(--purple-translucent); }
  .border-blue .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) { background: var(--blue-translucent); }
  .border-green .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) { background: var(--green-translucent); }
</style>

<section class="contact py-10 px-3 px-sm-4 px-md-5 full-height">
  <div class="mx-auto max-width-1200">

    <!-- Headline -->
    <div class="mb-5">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Get in Touch with the HIVE</h1>
      <p class="mb-0 lead">We’re here to answer your questions and guide you through our programs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-5">
      <!-- Left Column: Contact Form -->
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Send us a message</h2>

        <form class="needs-validation" novalidate data-contact-form action="/api/contact" method="post">
          <!-- Identify this form + timestamp + honeypot -->
          <input type="hidden" name="formType" value="contact" />
          <input type="hidden" name="ts" value="<%= Date.now() %>" />
          <div class="visually-hidden">
            <label for="company-contact">Company</label>
            <input type="text" id="company-contact" name="company" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="name" class="form-label mb-2">Name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control border-yellow outline-yellow" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your name.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="email" class="form-label mb-2">Email</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control border-purple outline-purple" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a valid email.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="phone" class="form-label mb-2">Phone</label>
            <input type="tel" class="form-control border-blue outline-blue" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(123) 456-7890">
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="subject" class="form-label mb-2">Subject</label>
            <select class="form-select border-green outline-green" id="subject" name="subject" aria-label="Select a topic">
              <option selected disabled>Select a topic</option>
              <option value="general">General inquiry</option>
              <option value="programs">Programs &amp; classes</option>
              <option value="partnership">Partnerships</option>
              <option value="support">Support</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
            <textarea class="form-control border-yellow outline-yellow" id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Write your message here..." required></textarea>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please include a message.</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Alerts (hidden by default) -->
          <div class="alert alert-success d-none" role="alert" data-success aria-live="polite">
            Thanks! We’ll be in touch shortly.
          </div>
          <div class="alert alert-danger d-none" role="alert" data-error aria-live="polite">
            Something went wrong. Please try again later.
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg bg-purple-gradient py-2 px-4">
            Send Message
            <span class="spinner-border spinner-border-sm align-middle ms-2 d-none" aria-hidden="true" data-spinner></span>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Info -->
      <div class="col-lg-5">
        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <h2 class="mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-telephone color-purple"></i> <a href="tel:+16198203475">(619) 820-3475</a></p>
        <p class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-envelope color-blue"></i> <a href="mailto:mignoneserviceemail@gmail.com">mignoneserviceemail@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <i class="bi bi-geo-alt color-green"></i>
          <a href="https://maps.google.com?q=1750+E+Palomar+St+Suite+7,+Chula+Vista,+CA+91913" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            1750 E. Palomar St. Suite 7, Chula Vista, CA
          </a>
        </p>

        <!-- Social Links -->
        <h2 class="mb-4 mt-5">Connect with us</h2>
        <div class="d-flex gap-4 mb-4">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-mignone-hive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="color-yellow bi bi-linkedin fs-2"></i></a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/themignonehive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="color-purple bi bi-instagram fs-2"></i></a>
          <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@themignonehive" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="TikTok"><i class="color-blue bi bi-tiktok fs-2"></i></a>
          <a href="https://x.com/themignonehive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="X (formerly Twitter)"><i class="color-green bi bi-twitter-x fs-2"></i></a>
        </div>

        <!-- Map -->
        <h2 class="mb-4 mt-5">Find Us</h2>
        <div class="ratio ratio-4x3 mb-2 rounded-4 overflow-hidden">
          <iframe
            title="Map to The Mignone HIVE"
            src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=1750+E+Palomar+St+Suite+7,+Chula+Vista,+CA+91913&output=embed"
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <!-- <a href="https://maps.google.com?q=1750+E+Palomar+St+Suite+7,+Chula+Vista,+CA+91913" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Get Directions
        </a> -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-5 pt-5">
      <div class="col-lg-5 order-lg-2">
        <!-- Hours -->
        <h2 class="mb-3">Business Hours</h2>
        <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
          <li>Mon – Fri: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM</li>
          <li>Saturday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM</li>
          <li>Sunday: Closed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-7 order-lg-1">
        <!-- Accessibility -->
        <h2 class="mb-3">Accessibility Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-0">Our facilities are wheelchair accessible, with accessible parking spaces near the entrance. Public transit stops are located within a 5-minute walk. If you need additional accommodations, please let us know in advance so we can assist you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="mt-5">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item border-yellow">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed outline-yellow" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
              How do I enroll in a program?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              You can enroll by reaching out through our contact form, email, or phone. Once we hear from you, we’ll share program dates and details to help you get started.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item border-purple">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
              What ages can join your programs?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Our programs are open to learners ages 3½ to 21. We also make exceptions for siblings of current students and for alumni who want to continue with us.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item border-blue">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
              Can I visit before enrolling?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Absolutely! Contact us to schedule a tour of our physical location.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 4 -->
        <div class="accordion-item border-green">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
              What is the scope of your work, and what happens during a typical session?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              At the Mignone HIVE, each session is shaped around the needs of the learner. Activities may include group outings, creative workshops, or skill-building classes that naturally weave in social and emotional growth. We also support families with in-home guidance and provide training that helps learners build confidence for both school and work.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 5 -->
        <div class="accordion-item border-yellow">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
              Where do your programs take place?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Our programs happen in a variety of settings to best support each learner. We have a physical location where sessions are held, along with community spaces like parks, libraries, beaches, and the zoo. Families can also receive virtual guidance at home, and older learners may join vocational training or internships that meet in places such as libraries or coffee shops.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 6 -->
        <div class="accordion-item border-purple">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq6">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
              What are the times and lengths of your programs?
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq6" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Schedules vary by student, but most classes and small outings take place on weekday evenings for about an hour. Families can also choose in-home support sessions scheduled around their availability, while vocational training follows each learner’s work schedule. Larger outings, like trips to the zoo or Balboa Park, are usually on weekends for a few hours, and we plan to add longer day camp options during school breaks.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
